.menu-toggle-label {
  display: none;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.menu {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu-ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu-item {
  position: relative;
}

.menu-item a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.menu-item a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
  background-color: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);
}

.menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  background-color: #0044cc;
  padding: 10px 0;
  list-style: none;
  min-width: 150px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.menu-item-has-children:hover .sub-menu {
  display: block;
}

.sub-menu li {
  margin: 5px 0;
}

.sub-menu a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
  display: block;
  padding: 5px 20px;
}

.sub-menu a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
  background-color: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .menu {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #0044cc;
    padding: 10px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 60px; /* Adjust based on header height */
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .menu-ul {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .menu-toggle-label {
    display: block;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .menu-toggle-checkbox:checked + .menu-toggle-label + .menu {
    display: flex;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
    position: static;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children:hover .sub-menu {
    display: none; /* Disable hover on mobile */
  }

  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
    display: none;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children:focus-within .sub-menu,
  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu:hover {
    display: block;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .mobile-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .mobile-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

.content-area {
  padding: 20px;
}

footer {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 10px;
  position: relative;
  /* No fixed positioning as per requirements */
}

.footer-content a {
  color: #ffcc00;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

.footer-content a:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

/* Additional Styling for Accessibility and Enhancements */

/* Focus States for Accessibility */
.menu-item a:focus,
.sub-menu a:focus {
  outline: 2px dashed #ffcc00;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Smooth Transition for Menu Toggle */
.menu {
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease-in-out;
}
```

### **Key Updates:**

1. **Class Name Alignment:**
   - Changed `.menu ul` to `.menu-ul` to match the `menu_class` defined in `header.php`.
   - Updated submenu selectors from `.submenu` to `.sub-menu` to align with WordPress's default submenu class.

2. **Responsive Menu Enhancements:**
   - Adjusted the mobile menu to position absolutely below the header.
   - Disabled hover effects on mobile to prevent unintended submenu displays.
   - Added focus states for better accessibility.

3. **Dynamic Hover Effects:**
   - Enhanced hover states to include background color changes for better visual feedback.

4. **Accessibility Improvements:**
   - Added focus outlines for keyboard navigation.
   - Ensured that interactive elements are easily navigable.

